project_info:
Concept

Capture the Flag involves two teams, each with a flag in his or her respective Base.
Capture the Flag is a objective-based competitive game where each team need a good
strategy, synergy and mechanics in order to win. Each team must play wisely and
cooperate with each of the team members to score point.
The game is a Bo3 (Best Of Three) style and a team must take 2 maps out of 3.

Gameplay

In order for a team to score, they must pick up the flag from the enemy base, and
subsequently return it to their own base. Your own team flag must be at base in order to
capture the enemy flag and score a point.
CTF (Capture The Flag) match is a Bo3 style, Each match between two team consist of
3 different maps. For a team to win they must win 2 out of 3 maps.
Team wins a map when they capture the enemy team 5 time.
Each team start at their base next to their Flag. Team can eliminate their opponents
using one of different types of weapon, each with his positive and negative stats.
project_abstract: Capture the Flag is a objective-based competitive game where each team need a good strategy, synergy and mechanics in order to win.
